member.example:
This sample shows how to call StatusAsync with required parameters.

var endpoint = new Uri("<https://my-service.azure.com>");
var client = new HttpbinClient(endpoint);

Response response = await client.StatusAsync(1234);
Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

